================================================================================
QUICK REFERENCE: THE PACKET TEST
================================================================================

DATA PACKET enters Licensed Software (Mobilytik, Visualytik, etc.)
  -- Was this packet generated by a controller running
     Project Sandstar + Sedona + Haystack?
       -- If YES: FREE USE
       -- If NO:  COMMERCIAL LICENSE REQUIRED

Scenario Guide
  - Building has only Sandstar controllers, app shows all data
        => YES - Free
  - Building has Sandstar + BACnet, app shows ONLY Sandstar data
        => YES - Free
  - Building has Sandstar + BACnet, app shows ALL data (unified view)
        => NO - Commercial license
  - BACnet data re-tagged as Haystack, fed to the app
        => NO - Commercial license (origin matters, not format)
  - SkySpark mixes sources, app queries ONLY Sandstar-origin records
        => YES - Free
  - SkySpark mixes sources, app queries all records
        => NO - Commercial license

